creator: WeMaster
descriptionHtml:
🤪 Get surprised and entertain yourself daily with this new displace puzzle game now!

Finding a fun and addictive puzzle game? Want to think in a more logical but creative way? Or are you the one who always wants to solve problems and come up with excellent solutions?

Welcome to DOP Story’s world! Here DOP Story’s inhabitants really need your help. Let’s displace one part and solve puzzles to support them!

🤯 DOP Story: Displace It!
- Train your brain in a light and fun way
- Drag and drop objects to solve riddles. Simple, right?!
- The game is so witty, funny, and incredibly creative that you'll want to share it with your friends and family right away.
- Blow all your stress away with 100+ puzzles- all are extremely entertaining and addictive
- Hilarious and inventive animations that you’ll love

🎮 How To Play
Each level, you will have half a picture upfront and a different accompanying task. Use your logic and imagination, drag and drop the given items below the picture to solve the riddles!
💡 The secret to victory:
- You must put the three items in the right place and in the right order.
- Sometimes, you don’t need to use all of given objects
- When feeling really stuck, you can click on the light bulb on the top right for a hint

Ready for an unique and endlessly surprising DOP puzzle game?

😲 Challenge Your Creativity
Believe it or not, give this puzzle solving game a try and you will be addicted to it!

Displacing objects to solve puzzles sounds easy, right? 😈😈😈 Honestly, it's not that simple.

To solve puzzles, sometimes you need to think in the craziest way. With this brain game, nothing is impossible. Download the game and you will be constantly surprised through each level we promise 😈

100+ Interesting Stories

Help a girl turn into a mermaid, help the wife catch her husband cheating or help 3 boys sneak into the cinema…We have designed 100+ puzzles with weird and hilarious situations waiting for you to explore.

🧠 Practice Logical Thinking
To complete each riddle, you need to put the items in the correct order.
Your ability to reason logically will improve dramatically even while you are playing entertainment. Give your logic a real workout 💪 without ever driving you absolutely crazy. Wonderful, isn't it?

🔥 Super Fun And Addictive
You’ll find it amusing and creative at the same time. Plus, clear and colorful graphics with calm, happy music will boost your mood.

Download DOP Story: Displace it now and become a real displace master!

descriptionHtml:
🤪 Get surprised and entertain yourself daily with this new displace puzzle game now!

Finding a fun and addictive puzzle game? Want to be more logical and creative? Try thinking out of a box with this game.

Welcome to DOP Story’s world! More than 200+ fun puzzles are waiting for you. Let’s displace one part and solve puzzles!

🤯 DOP Story: Displace It!
- Train your brain in a light and fun way.Sometimes, you need to be witty 😈
- Drag and drop objects to solve riddles. Simple, right?!
- The game is so witty, funny, and incredibly creative that you'll want to share it with your friends and family right away.
- Blow all your stress away with 200+ puzzles- all are extremely entertaining and addictive
- Hilarious and inventive animations that you’ll love

🎮 How To Play
Each level, you will have half a picture upfront and a different accompanying task. Use your logic and imagination, drag and drop the given items below the picture to solve the riddles!
💡 The secret to victory:
- You must put the three items in the right place and in the right order.
- Sometimes, you don’t need to use all of given objects
- When feeling really stuck, you can click on the light bulb on the top right for a hint

Ready for an unique and endlessly surprising DOP puzzle game?

😲 Challenge Your Creativity
Believe it or not, give this puzzle solving game a try and you will be addicted to it!

Displacing objects to solve puzzles sounds easy, right? 😈😈😈 Honestly, it's not that simple.

To solve puzzles, sometimes you need to think in the craziest way. With this brain game, nothing is impossible. Download the game and you will be constantly surprised through each level we promise 😈

200+ Interesting Puzzles

Help a girl turn into a mermaid, help the wife catch her husband cheating or help 3 boys sneak into the cinema…We have designed 200+ puzzles with weird and hilarious situations waiting for you to explore.

🧠 Practice Logical Thinking
To complete each riddle, you need to put the items in the correct order.
Your ability to reason logically will improve dramatically even while you are playing entertainment. Give your logic a real workout 💪 without ever driving you absolutely crazy. Wonderful, isn't it?

🔥 Super Fun And Addictive
You’ll find it amusing and creative at the same time. Plus, clear and colorful graphics with calm, happy music will boost your mood.

Download DOP Story: Displace it now and become a real Displace master!
